room_title: Escape room "Th3 C0d3" by Escapology Tewksbury in Boston
review: Took my wife for her birthday yesterday. We had a great time and solved the mystery! We'll definitely be going back again!

room_title: Escape room "Th3 C0d3" by Escapology Tewksbury in Boston
review: This was my first time trying an escape room and I loved it! Charlie, our game master, was excellent at giving us the hints we needed to help us along the way! It's also great that they have a fully stocked bar! Not sure if the booze helped or hindered our solve time. We did TH3 C0D3, which is rated as the second EASIEST! Can't wait to go back and try more!
